Package: perk
Type: Package
Title: Robust permutation tests of correlation coefficients
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Han Yu, Alan Hutson
Maintainer: Han Yu <han.yu@roswellpark.org>
Description: Robust permutation test of Pearson correlation coefficient, Spearman correlation coefficient, and Lin's concordance correlation coefficient. The tests robustly controls type I error under general scenarios when sample size is small and two variables are dependent but uncorrelated. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
